  "releaseBoundary": "A green source matrix does not establish installed-runtime or publication readiness. Issues 37, 53, and 92 remain the runtime promotion and readback carriers. Issue 86 remains the complete reusable child-page and template-library carrier. Manual assistive-technology and physical-device verification remains required after the automated installed harness passes."
